rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0010
rows.name: Kylie, what's that you're up to there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0030
rows.name: I was just about to head out to meet Omomo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0060
rows.name:
I just had a message from her, asking for help
with her luggage. She says she can't carry it alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0090
rows.name: I know she'd been planning on staying here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0110
rows.name: I thought I knew better than she did...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0130
rows.name: she'd done some thinking, about what you told her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0140
rows.name:
Like, she'd fallen into this mistaken feeling
that she had to rely on others,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0150
rows.name:
and she felt that she was running away
from her own responsibilities. Heh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0200
rows.name: I had a hunch that Omomo might not want to come...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0210
rows.name:
But it's like, every time we met,
she always seemed to act so zen...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0250
rows.name: And, in the end, Lin managed to get through to her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0270
rows.name: No, it really is all thanks to you, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0280
rows.name: If it was me, I'd have just listened to her talk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0290
rows.name: I wouldn't have been able to speak my mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0310
rows.name:
How important it is to say what you're feeling.
What it achieves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0330
rows.name: Kylie, please! You're making me self-conscious...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0370
rows.name: Go on now, don't keep Omomo waiting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32260100_MSG0390
rows.name: Everyone, thanks so very much, again![ST:wait ]
